      "rdf:value": "<L>7<pc>1-0003<k1>aMSa<k2>a/MSa<h>1\n1. {#a/MSa#}¦ (<ab>s.</ab> <is>gaṇa</is> {#vfzAdi#}) <lex>m.</lex>\n<ls>SIDDH. K. 249,b, ult.</ls>\n<div n=\"1\"> 1) {%Theil%}\n<ls>AK. 2,9,90.</ls>\n<ls>H. 1434.</ls>\n<div n=\"2\">— a) {%Theil, Abschnitt%}\n<ls>H. an. 2,542.</ls> ({#ekadeSe vastunaH#}): {#zoqaSoM 'SaH#} ({#candrasya#}) {#kalA#} {%der 16te Theil (des Mondes) heisst%} <is>kalā</is>\n<ls>H. 106.</ls> {#tUryaMSa#} {%der 4te Theil%}\n<ls>AK. 3,4,92.</ls> {#aMSo 'zwamo 'hniH#} {%der 8te Abschnitt, die%}\n[Page1-0004]\n{%8te Stunde des%} (15stündigen) {%Tages%}\n<ls>AK. 2,7,31.</ls> {#zazWamaMSaM pradadyAtpEtfkAdDanAt#} {%den 6ten Theil gebe er vom väterlichen Vermögen%}\n<ls>M. 9,164.</ls> {#mamEvAMSaH#} {%ein Theil von mir%}\n<ls>BHAG. 15,7.</ls>\n<div n=\"2\">— b) {%ein Theil des Kaufpreises, Haftgeld%}: {#A na\\stuja^M ra\\yiM Ba\\rAMSa\\M na pra^tijAna\\te#}\n<ls>ṚV. 3,45,4.</ls>\n<div n=\"2\">— c) {%Antheil%}: {#udinnva^sya ricyate\\ aMSo\\ Dana\\M na ji\\gyuza^H#}\n<ls>ṚV. 7,32,12.</ls> {#aDA^yi DI\\tirasa^sfgra\\maMSA^H#}\n<ls n=\"ṚV.\">10,31,3.</ls> <ls>AV. 11,1,5.</ls> {#taddAsEreva dAtavyaM svatoM 'SataH#}\n<ls>M. 8,408.</ls> {%Erbschaftsantheil%}: {#anaMSO klIvapatitO#}\n<ls>M. 9,201.</ls> {#niraMSaka#} {%ohne Erbtheil bleibend%}\n<ls>YĀJÑ. 2,140.</ls> {#patnyaH kAryAH samAMSikAH#}\n<ls n=\"YĀJÑ.\">2,115.</ls>\n<div n=\"2\">— d) {%Partei%}: {#a\\smAka\\maMSa\\muda^vA\\ Bare^ Bare#}\n<ls>ṚV. 1,102,4.</ls> <ls n=\"ṚV. 1,\">112,1.</ls>\n<div n=\"2\">— e) {%Nenner eines Bruchs%}\n<ls>COLEBR. Alg. 13.</ls>\n<div n=\"1\">— 2) {%Theilung, Erbschaftstheilung%}\n<ls>H. an. 2,542.</ls> {#(viBAjane): sakfdaMSo nipatati#}\n<ls>M. 9,47.</ls> = <ls>SĀV. 2,26.</ls>\n<div n=\"1\">— 3) Name eines <is>Āditya</is> ({%Theilnehmer, Vertheiler%}\n<ls>ROTH</ls> in <ls>Z. d. d. m. G. VI,75.</ls>): {#tvamaMSo^ vi\\daTe^ deva BAja\\yuH#} (<is>Agni</is>)\n<ls>ṚV. 2,1,4.</ls> <ls n=\"ṚV. 2,\">27,1.</ls> <ls n=\"ṚV.\">5,42,5.</ls>\n<ls>VS. 10,5.</ls>\n<ls>AV. 6,2,5.</ls> <ls n=\"AV.\">11,17,2.</ls> Name des 6ten <is>Āditya</is>,\n<ls>MBH. 1,2523.</ls> des 11ten, <ls>HARIV. 176.</ls> <ls>VP.</ls> des 5ten,\n<ls>MIT. 142,3.</ls> des 9ten,\n<ls>HARIV. 12456.</ls> — Es kommt auch die Schreibart {#aMsa#} <ab>vor.</ab>\n<LEND>"
